import React from 'react';
import { Link as RouterLink } from 'react-router-dom';
import {
  Box,
  Container,
  Grid as MuiGrid,
  Typography,
  Link,
  IconButton,
  Divider,
} from '@mui/material';
import { styled } from '@mui/material/styles';
import {
  Facebook,
  Twitter,
  LinkedIn,
  Instagram,
} from '@mui/icons-material';

// Properly typed Grid components for MUI compatibility
const Grid = styled(MuiGrid)(({ theme }) => ({}));
Grid.defaultProps = { container: false };

const GridContainer = ({ children, ...props }) => (
  <Grid container {...props}>{children}</Grid>
);

const GridItem = ({ children, ...props }) => (
  <Grid {...props}>{children}</Grid>
);

const Footer = () => {
  return (
    <Box
      component="footer"
      sx={{
        bgcolor: 'background.paper',
        py: 6,
        mt: 'auto',
      }}
    >
      <Container maxWidth="lg">
        <GridContainer spacing={4}>
          <GridItem xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
            <Typography variant="h6" color="primary" gutterBottom>
              AgriWaste Market
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
              Transforming agricultural waste into valuable resources through our B2B marketplace.
            </Typography>
            <Box sx={{ mt: 2 }}>
              <IconButton color="primary">
                <Facebook />
              </IconButton>
              <IconButton color="primary">
                <Twitter />
              </IconButton>
              <IconButton color="primary">
                <LinkedIn />
              </IconButton>
              <IconButton color="primary">
                <Instagram />
              </IconButton>
            </Box>
          </GridItem>

          <GridItem xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
            <Typography variant="h6" color="text.primary" gutterBottom>
              Quick Links
            </Typography>
            <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', gap: 1 }}>
              <Link component={RouterLink} to="/marketplace" color="inherit">
                Marketplace
              </Link>
              <Link component={RouterLink} to="/about" color="inherit">
                About Us
              </Link>
              <Link component={RouterLink} to="/contact" color="inherit">
                Contact
              </Link>
              <Link component={RouterLink} to="/faq" color="inherit">
                FAQ
              </Link>
            </Box>
          </GridItem>

          <GridItem xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
            <Typography variant="h6" color="text.primary" gutterBottom>
              Categories
            </Typography>
            <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', gap: 1 }}>
              <Link component={RouterLink} to="/marketplace?category=crop-residue" color="inherit">
                Crop Residue
              </Link>
              <Link component={RouterLink} to="/marketplace?category=animal-waste" color="inherit">
                Animal Waste
              </Link>
              <Link component={RouterLink} to="/marketplace?category=food-processing" color="inherit">
                Food Processing Waste
              </Link>
              <Link component={RouterLink} to="/marketplace?category=forestry" color="inherit">
                Forestry Waste
              </Link>
            </Box>
          </GridItem>

          <GridItem xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
            <Typography variant="h6" color="text.primary" gutterBottom>
              Contact Us
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
              Email: info@agriwastemarket.com
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
              Phone: +91 98765 43210
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
              Address: 123 Agro Business Park,
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
              New Delhi, India - 110001
            </Typography>
          </GridItem>
        </GridContainer>

        <Divider sx={{ my: 4 }} />

        <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'space-between', alignItems: 'center' }}>
          <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
            © {new Date().getFullYear()} AgriWaste Market. All rights reserved.
          </Typography>
          <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', gap: 2 }}>
            <Link component={RouterLink} to="/privacy" color="inherit">
              Privacy Policy
            </Link>
            <Link component={RouterLink} to="/terms" color="inherit">
              Terms of Service
            </Link>
          </Box>
        </Box>
      </Container>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Footer;
